    "steps": [
      "Define a continuous-time state-space model using mc.ss",
      "Convert the system to discrete-time using mc.c2d",
      "Set the reference vector, horizon predict constant, and horizon time constant",
      "Set the regularization parameter for smoother inputs",
      "Simulate linear programming MPC using mc.lmpc",
      "Plot the input signal over time",
      "Define integral action constant, maximum input signal vector, and slack variables",
      "Simulate quadratic programming MPC using mc.qmpc"
