    "theory": "Model Predictive Control (MPC) implementation using Linear Programming (LMPC) and Quadratic Programming (QMPC). The QMPC implementation includes a Kalman-Bucy filter and a unique integral action where the integral is added to the reference vector for microcontroller implementation.",
